\zeta(z)=\frac{1}{\Gamma(z)}\int_0^\infty\frac{t^{z-1}}{e^t-1}dt=\frac{\Gamma(z-1)}{2\pi i}\int_{-\infty}^0\frac{t^{z-1}}{e^{-t}-1}dt
\frac{1}{e^t-1}=\sum_{m=0}^{\infty}B_m\frac{t^{m-1}}{m!}
